	* progmodes/grep.el (grep-filter): Don't trip on partial lines.

	* shell.el (shell-completion-vars): New function.
	(shell-mode):
	* simple.el (read-shell-command): Use it.
	(blink-matching-open): No need for " [...]" in minibuffer-message.

