2011-04-06  Chong Yidong  <cyd@stupidchicken.com>

	* emacs-lisp/cconv.el (cconv--analyse-use): Ignore "ignored" when
	issuing unused warnings.

	* emacs-lisp/tabulated-list.el (tabulated-list-print): Use lambda
	macro directly.

